text.tspan: Divine, O Son of God, art Thou,
In Thee God’s fulness find we now.
Divine, O Son of God, art Thou,
In Thee God’s fulness find we now.
But the high mysteries of Thy Name
Divine, O Son of God, art Thou,
In Thee God’s fulness find we now.
Th’ eternal theme of praise is this,
Divine, O Son of God, art Thou,
In Thee God’s fulness find we now.
